
### BODY RECEIVER ###
--- readClient only accepts headers
------- bytes read from body are stored
---- read operation is always non blocking
-------- meaning that body receiver keeps state, returns when reading not possible anymore
-------- next select call continue reading body


### MUST HAVE FEATURES ###
- Socket: timeout op Server level (configuren in config.json)
- CGI: optimization read / write
- Receiver: module die message body ontvangt
------- Chunked decoding

#### BUGS ####
--- route names ( /directory/ ) fixen, laatste slash

###### TESTER #######
--- CGI: env PATH_INFO not set
--- CGI: env REQUEST_URI not same as PATH - QUERY.
------ https://stackoverflow.com/questions/279966/php-self-vs-path-info-vs-script-name-vs-request-uri
--- CGI: niet standaard chunked returnen ?
------- output ubuntu_cgi_tester is al voorzien van CRLF

### EXTRA ####
- Proxy: support toevoegen voor client body in request
- Directory: DirListing met .. voor traversal
- Config: default error pages
